Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:58.96,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}燦然と輝く街の灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.40,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}対照的な僕を見下ろす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.34,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}あのビルの間を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.23,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}色付き出したネオンと混じって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.16,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}僕の時間とこの世界をトレード
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.02,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}夜に沈む
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.30,0:19:58.96,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}街道上灯光璀璨闪耀
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.40,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}与被轻视的我形成鲜明对照
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.34,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}行于灯红酒绿的间隙
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.23,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}被逐一亮起的霓虹灯所吞噬
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.16,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}以我的时间换取我的存在
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.02,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H37C0CD&\blur5\fad(300,300)}随后沉沦于夜色
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,### Insert「キュート.メドレー ~アイドル サウンズ~」
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,{=621}最最最最  最喜欢了
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,你倒是给我告白呀
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,嘴上这么答应着但是
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,冷酷的
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,散漫的节拍
Comment: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:10.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,让我听听吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,### Insert「もーいいかい」
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:30.86,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}ずっと息をしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.86,0:46:33.02,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}何も解らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.03,0:46:35.45,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}知らない知らないばかり 嗚呼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.45,0:46:37.15,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}漂う後悔透明です
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.16,0:46:38.94,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}もうすっかり見えないな
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.94,0:46:41.25,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}笑ってもいいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.25,0:46:43.69,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}涙ぽつり零れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.69,0:46:45.31,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}いつまで経っても夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.31,0:46:47.78,Insert 12 - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}なら少し止まってもいいじゃんか
Dialogue: 1,0:46:29.11,0:46:30.86,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}一直在呼吸着
Dialogue: 1,0:46:30.86,0:46:33.02,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}什么都不理解
Dialogue: 1,0:46:33.03,0:46:35.45,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}全是些不知道不知道 哇哈
Dialogue: 1,0:46:35.45,0:46:37.15,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}漂浮着的后悔那么透明
Dialogue: 1,0:46:37.16,0:46:38.94,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}现在已经完全看不清了
Dialogue: 1,0:46:38.94,0:46:41.25,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}可以露出笑容吗
Dialogue: 1,0:46:41.25,0:46:43.69,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}为了不让眼泪滴落下来
Dialogue: 1,0:46:43.69,0:46:45.31,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}不管过了多久都在沉浸在梦中
Dialogue: 1,0:46:45.31,0:46:47.78,Insert 12 - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur5\fad(300,300)}那么稍微停下来也没事吧
